      <title>亿万富翁“法国默多克”让勒庞的政治正常化</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-03/vincent-bollore-billionaire-french-murdoch-who-has-helped-le-pen-s-rise</link>
      <description><![CDATA[玛丽娜·勒庞领导的极右翼国民联盟在周日的法国大选中成为领跑者，这与亿万富翁文森特·博洛雷 (Vincent Bolloré) 支持的强大保守媒体机器的出现密切相关，文森特·博洛雷被称为“法国默多克”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-03/vincent-bollore-billionaire-french-murdoch-who-has-helped-le-pen-s-rise</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 03 Jul 2024 04:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
