      <title>马来西亚法院驳回纳吉布因 1MDB 罪名申请软禁</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-03/malaysia-court-rejects-najib-s-house-arrest-plea-for-1mdb-crime</link>
      <description><![CDATA[马来西亚法院驳回了前总理纳吉布拉扎克因与问题财富基金 1MDB 相关的罪行而提出的在家中服完剩余刑期的请求。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-03/malaysia-court-rejects-najib-s-house-arrest-plea-for-1mdb-crime</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 03 Jul 2024 02:05:10 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>工党重获英国政权的五种方式</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-02/five-ways-labour-can-get-back-to-power-in-the-uk</link>
      <description><![CDATA[为期六周的大选活动让英国的民意调查结果非常一致：预计反对党工党将获胜，党魁基尔·斯塔默将成为英国新任首相。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-02/five-ways-labour-can-get-back-to-power-in-the-uk</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 02 Jul 2024 23:01:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>阿塞拜疆因亚美尼亚武器供应升级与法国太平洋冲突</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-02/azerbaijan-escalates-conflict-with-france-over-armenia-arms-supply</link>
      <description><![CDATA[阿塞拜疆与法国之间的冲突不断升级，冲突范围蔓延至太平洋、加勒比海和拉丁美洲的法国领土，原因是法国向亚美尼亚提供了武器。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-02/azerbaijan-escalates-conflict-with-france-over-armenia-arms-supply</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 02 Jul 2024 23:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>加拿大考虑封锁工厂以抵制中国电动汽车</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-02/canada-to-consider-blocking-factories-in-pushback-on-chinese-evs</link>
      <description><![CDATA[加拿大总理贾斯汀·特鲁多领导的政府已经公布了将考虑采取的阻止中国制造的电动汽车进入加拿大市场的措施，包括对进口产品征收关税以及阻止中国在加拿大新工厂的投资。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-02/canada-to-consider-blocking-factories-in-pushback-on-chinese-evs</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 02 Jul 2024 22:53:47 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
