    <item>
      <title>米莱在“恐龙”话题中为玻利维亚和巴西的观点辩护</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-02/milei-defends-bolivia-brazil-views-ahead-of-brazil-visit</link>
      <description><![CDATA[阿根廷总统哈维尔·米莱在社交媒体帖子中为自己对上周玻利维亚政变企图的怀疑进行辩护，并继续攻击巴西总统路易斯·伊纳西奥·卢拉·达席尔瓦，称一位未透露姓名的批评者是“白痴恐龙”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-02/milei-defends-bolivia-brazil-views-ahead-of-brazil-visit</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 02 Jul 2024 16:46:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国扣押台湾渔船或加剧紧张局势</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-02/china-seizes-taiwan-fishing-boat-and-crew-as-tensions-simmer</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国扣押了一艘台湾渔船及其船员，此举有可能加剧与台湾新总统的紧张关系。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-02/china-seizes-taiwan-fishing-boat-and-crew-as-tensions-simmer</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 02 Jul 2024 16:25:50 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>拜登将辩论表现不佳归咎于时差，希望平息抗议</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-02/biden-to-meet-democratic-governors-as-he-looks-to-close-ranks</link>
      <description><![CDATA[总统乔·拜登将自己在与唐纳德·特朗普的灾难性辩论前几周前往法国和意大利的旅行计划归咎于他在舞台上的糟糕表现，试图解释这一颠覆 2024 年大选并危及他连任前景的时刻。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-02/biden-to-meet-democratic-governors-as-he-looks-to-close-ranks</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 02 Jul 2024 16:25:09 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国和菲律宾试图缓解海上紧张局势</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-02/china-philippines-hold-talks-after-sea-clash-in-june-rappler</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在两国发生最严重的海上冲突之一之后的会晤中，中国和菲律宾外交官同意缓解南海紧张局势，但坚持各自的主权主张。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-02/china-philippines-hold-talks-after-sea-clash-in-june-rappler</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 02 Jul 2024 08:48:04 GMT</pubDate>
